description:
The one who possesses the Teacher's Memorandum shall being peace to the World of the Martial Arts academies... but what exactly is the Teacher's Memorandum? The story before the hit MTV original movie! Volcano High pushes the limits of imagination as super-powered martial arts students battle for supremacy and the possession of the ultimate prize - The Teacher's Memorandum!

Chapter Titles

  • Chapter 1: Teacher's Memorandum
  • Chapter 2: Pine Forest, Sole Crane
  • Chapter 3: Lightning & Thunder, The Academy Five

description: What happens after Clark puts on the costume? Can he keep his Super-secret quiet? Pere Perez illustrates Bryan Q. Miller's story in the first chapter of this ongoing series.
name: Guardian Chapter 1

description: Nico Macchia takes place, with great historical and visual accuracy, at the end of the sixteenth century, an era characterized by deep religious conflicts. The book tells the story of three knights of fortune: Nico Macchia, exiled from Ferrara, his birthplace; Conghe Dommert, a Landsknecht who left their companions, and Mal Mouhal Assad, an Ottoman army deserter.
name: Nico Macchia
